.TH "sw_get_addr" 9 "sw_get_addr" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
sw_get_addr \- get the switch MAC address.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" sw_get_addr
.BI "(struct ksz_hw *hw "  ","
.BI "u8 *mac_addr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "hw" 12
The hardware instance.
.IP "mac_addr" 12
Buffer to store the MAC address.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This function retrieves the MAC address of the switch.
